@milner_31 on Hattah 2021

#RaceOrange #ReadyToRace #KTM #alpinestars #astarsmx21 #alpinestarsaustralia #alpinestarsprotects

Helicopter: @tomanderson22 @joshanderson193

MB01YIQCS5FCFAB

Repost via: @alpinestars_racing_aus

node.text:
See what it takes to make 2 custom @motogp suits for @garrettgerloff at our production racing facility in Italy and then transport the suits to Holland on time for FP1! 

This valiant effort takes the focused talents of over 20 skilled staff members to make this happen, all sewn by hand utilizing Alpinestars top protection materials and technology. 

ONE GOAL ONE VISION ONE TEAM 

#AlpinestarsProtects #OneGoalOneVision #ThinkingAhead #RacingAhead

node.title: Follow The Journey! Behind the scenes at Alpinestars.

node.text:
Thank you Valentino for all you have brought to our motorcycling world that we all love.  We have seen you love riding motorcycles since you were very young, your love for being in the paddock, we saw your infinite passion for racing no matter how much you had already achieved. 

You have represented our sport in a spontaneous amazing way and we know that you always will.  We look forward to continuing to see you in the racing paddock, on motorcycles or cars or any form of motorsports as true passion never stops.

Thank you for everything Vale,

Alpinestars.

Alpinestars new “GP Force Chaser” 1 piece leather suit. 

Track or performance riders looking for class leading leather suit protection with a inviting price point? Seek no further. 

Astars Quick Facts:

This suit comes Tech Air 5 ready with strategically positioned accordion stretch panel inserts. 

Calf expansion panel with stretch ribs for a custom fit.

Stretch panels on abdomen, under the arms, on the arms, crotch and back of leg for an optimum high performance riding fit and help to fit a large range of riders sizes and shapes. 

Pricing: $899.95 
Sizes: 38-64 euro. 
2 color options.

Motivation Monday with @jakegagne as he made history this past weekend as the first rider to win 11 consecutive races in the Superbike Class. The previous record was held by his former teammate Cameron Beaubier and Josh Hayes. 

In race 1 Jake even had a low side in the opening laps causing a red flag, they restarted the race and he won. 🏁

Congratulations Jake and the rest of the @attackyamaha team.
